<body>
<header>
  <h1>SACI Paper Clean View</h1>
  <p>Okunabilir makale diyagramları, senaryo bazlı interaktif çıktı ve tam graph bağlantıları.</p>
</header>

<main>

<section class="card nonprint">
  <div class="kpis">
    <div class="kpi">
      <div class="label">Toplam senaryo</div>
      <div class="value" id="k-scenarios">-</div>
    </div>
    <div class="kpi">
      <div class="label">S8 SACI</div>
      <div class="value" id="k-s8">-</div>
    </div>
    <div class="kpi">
      <div class="label">S8 missing edge</div>
      <div class="value" id="k-missing">-</div>
    </div>
    <div class="kpi">
      <div class="label">Açıklama katmanı</div>
      <div class="value" style="font-size:22px">Policy-guided</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="card nonprint">
  <div class="tabs">
    <button class="active" onclick="showPanel('model', this)">Model</button>
    <button onclick="showPanel('closure', this)">S8 closure</button>
    <button onclick="showPanel('criticality', this)">Criticality</button>
    <button onclick="showPanel('missing', this)">S7A missing</button>
    <button onclick="showPanel('taxonomy', this)">Taxonomy</button>
    <button onclick="showPanel('matrix', this)">Fault matrix</button>
    <button onclick="showPanel('scenario', this)">Scenario detail</button>
    <button onclick="showPanel('table', this)">Full table</button>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="model" class="panel active card">
  <div class="paper">
    <h2>SACI Conceptual Model</h2>

    <div class="flow">
      <div class="node blue">Assets<br>DC / endpoint / firewall</div>
      <div class="node orange">Log sources<br>Security / Sysmon / PowerShell / authlog / firewall</div>
      <div class="node green">Detection controls<br>expected visibility rules</div>
      <div class="node red">Wazuh rules<br>observed alerts</div>
    </div>

    <div class="arrow-row">
      <div>asset inventory</div>
      <div>telemetry collection</div>
      <div>control evidence</div>
      <div>alert evidence</div>
    </div>

    <div class="flow">
      <div class="node purple">MITRE ATT&CK<br>technique coverage</div>
      <div class="node cyan">CTI / MISP<br>IOC closure</div>
      <div class="node yellow">SACI metrics<br>LC / CAC / MDC / CTIC / TF</div>
      <div class="node green big">SACI score<br>deterministic visibility score</div>
    </div>

    <div class="flow-3">
      <div class="node gray">Graph relation state<br>observed / missing</div>
      <div class="node cyan">Policy-guided explanation<br>explains outputs<br>does not calculate score</div>
      <div class="node yellow">Human-readable report<br>scenario-level interpretation</div>
    </div>

    <div class="note">
      SACI does not decide whether an organization is secure. It measures whether expected visibility relationships are observable.
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="closure" class="panel card">
  <div class="paper">
    <h2>S8 Final Visibility Closure</h2>

    <div class="flow">
      <div class="node blue">A04 / WS01<br>Windows endpoint</div>
      <div class="node orange">Security<br>Sysmon<br>PowerShell logs</div>
      <div class="node green">Controls C023-C027<br>seen=1</div>
      <div class="node red">Wazuh rules<br>110240-110244</div>
    </div>

    <div class="flow">
      <div class="node red">Wazuh SIEM<br>alerts observed</div>
      <div class="node purple">MITRE coverage<br>T1078 / T1087<br>T1071.004 / T1016</div>
      <div class="node cyan">CTI closure<br>IOC evidence converted to alert</div>
      <div class="node green big" id="closure-result">S8 final closure</div>
    </div>

    <div class="note">
      This is a simplified evidence path. The full evidence graph remains available as an interactive supplementary artifact.
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="criticality" class="panel card">
  <div class="paper">
    <h2>Critical vs Non-critical Telemetry Loss</h2>

    <div class="compare">
      <div class="compare-card red">
        <div class="node red big" id="crit-s7a">S7A</div>
